{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2191552, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 424558, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "dz现在特别喜欢小朋友，支教两次了\n", "timestamp": 1627895221, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2191563, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 424558, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这波改革以后怕不是会有很多幺蛾子", "timestamp": 1627895338, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2191581, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 424558, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有，找那种初高中同校的，带完初三申请去带高一。\n但yysy初中和高中差老远呢，支教和真正带课也差老远呢，你确定能在批不完的作业、上不完的课、听不完的唠叨、管不完的学生、烦死人的领导、不一定和谐的备课组的重重压力下，依然保持着对于小朋友的“喜欢”以及对于中学教育的初衷吗？", "timestamp": 1627895429, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2191583, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 424558, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这跨度也太大了点", "timestamp": 1627895433, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2191594, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 424558, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "还有半夜打电话的家长、晚上11点半才下的晚自习、早上7点就要到的早读、不那么高的薪资", "timestamp": 1627895500, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2191624, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 424558, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "当然，以上的问题在支教中完全不存在，因为支教属于志愿行为，不需要对学生负责。但是教师就不一样了，教师身上的责任很重；如果你为了追求奖金或者更高的薪资，或者是被上级看中了，当了班主任、备课组长、年级组长，需要背负的东西就更多了。\n\n好奇一下dz考虑过这些很现实的问题吗🤔", "timestamp": 1627895699, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2191632, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 424558, "reply_to": 2191594, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: bob说的也确实，支教可能是要欢乐一些相比真正的教学，但或许俺可以先尝试下\n", "timestamp": 1627895756, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2191649, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 424558, "reply_to": 2191624, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: quq，还真没想那么深，但教师相比其它的工作，可能更pure一点吧（我猜的）", "timestamp": 1627895880, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2191650, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 424558, "reply_to": 2191632, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: dz或许可以先和自己初高中的老师聊聊，看看他们的想法？或者身边去当中学老师的师兄师姐们，如果有的话也聊一聊。", "timestamp": 1627895878, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2191660, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 424558, "reply_to": 2191650, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 嗯，谢谢热心Bob\n", "timestamp": 1627895950, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2191661, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 424558, "reply_to": 2191660, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 加油！", "timestamp": 1627895961, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2191878, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 424558, "reply_to": 2191552, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 哪里有支教带我一起呗", "timestamp": 1627897706, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2192856, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 424558, "reply_to": 2191878, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 哈哈哈，都是碰见合适的支队招募，然后就加了\n", "timestamp": 1627908834, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 2, "pid": 424558, "reply": 13, "tag": null, "text": "以后想当老师，但是想从初一一直带到高三，能有这种机会吗？还有洞友们觉得当老师怎么样呀？dz男", "timestamp": 1627895186, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1627908836, "url": "", "vote": {}}}